Package: xubamp
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: native Wayland audio player with classic skin support
 xubamp decodes MP3 and WAV audio, sends it to PipeWire, and renders
 classic Winamp skin archives on Wayland.
